dct_title_s: The Seat of War in Turkey
dct_description_sm: Published by Edward Stanford, Ltd., 12, 13, & 14, Long Acre, W.C. ; Reproduced in photographic rooms War College Division, General Staff.
Legend indicates submarine telegraph cables, railways (proposed and open).
Also shows various roads, waterways, canals, wells, miscellaneous locations (ruins, pyramids, salt).
Descriptive text, such as "a continuous desert of Red Sand."
dct_creator_sm: United States, War Department., General Staff., War College Division.
